room_title: Escape room "Head Trip" by ArtHatch Escape in San Marcos (CA)
room_description: One day, the Botanist, known for his eccentric art collection and fascination with psychedelics, reached true enlightenment. After drifting too far into the psychedelic macrocosm, the Botanist was caught somewhere between life and death. His son, the Birthday Boy, needs your help to bring his father back to our realm before he is lost forever!
